yy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Faerosmith-tickets%2Fartist%2F734396" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>查找所有巡演日期和任何剩余门票。</p><p>在 Aerosmith 的其他新闻中，上个月有报道称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chris-daughtry-approached-sing-for-aerosmith-joe-perry-steven-tyler-3483561">Chris Daughtry 曾被邀请为 Aerosmith 演唱</a>，取代这位标志性主唱。</p><p>多特里在<em>戴夫·里卡兹</em>播客的采访中透露了这一消息，并表示乔·佩里曾打电话给他来代替史蒂文·泰勒参加一系列节目。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-aerosmith-kick-off-farewell-tour-with-fleetwood-mac-cover-and-first-performance-of-adams-apple-in-five-years-3492835">《Watch Aerosmith》以弗利特伍德麦克 (Fleetwood Mac) 封面为告别巡演拉开序幕，五年来首次表演《亚当的苹果》 (Adam&#39;s Apple)</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《Starfield》DLSS 模组引发付费模组争议https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/starfield-dlss-mod-sparks-controversy-over-paid-modding-3492782?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=starfield-dlss-mod-sparks-controversy-过度付费改装Imogen DonovanMon, 04 Sep 2023 09:15:12 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsModsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3492782 <p><img width="1252" height="795" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-mod-controversy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-mod-controversy.jpg 1252w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-mod-controversy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-mod-controversy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-mod-controversy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-mod-controversy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" /></p><p>这场争论让人想起《天际》付费模组的崩溃</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/starfield-dlss-mod-sparks-controversy-over-paid-modding-3492782">《Starfield》DLSS 模组</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上，引发了有关付费模组的争议。</p> ; <p><img width="1252" height="795" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-mod-controversy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-mod-controversy.jpg 1252w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-mod-controversy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-mod-controversy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-mod-controversy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-mod-controversy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/starfield"><em>Starfield</em></a>社区被分割为一个在游戏中添加 DLSS 的付费模组，该模组已被“破解”，或者换句话说，在没有创建者对其施加限制的情况下重新分发。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/life-by-you-will-let-the-sims-fans-live-their-best-and-worst-lives-3491488">“Life By You”将让“模拟人生”粉丝过上最好（和最坏）的生活</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/nvidia">Nvidia</a>的 DLSS（深度学习超级采样）使用人工智能进行抗锯齿、帧生成和光线重建，使游戏在玩家的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/pc">PC</a>上看起来尽可能出色。</p><p>出乎意料的是，人们发现<em>Starfield</em>不支持 DLSS，但没过多久，改装者就将此事掌握在自己手中。 PureDark 的 DLSS 2 mod 可通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/nexus-mods">Nexus Mods</a><a href="https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/111/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">免费下载</a>，但是，他们的 DLSS 3 mod 仅在玩家为 Patreon 付费后才可用。</p><p>更重要的是，DLSS 3 mod 具有 DRM（数字版权管理）保护 - 一个身份验证请求，以确保人们在不先订阅 PureDark 的情况下无法访问该 mod。 </p><figure id="attachment_3491508" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3491508" style="width: 1252px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3491508" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-fans-are-smart-2.jpg" alt="" width="1252" height="795" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-fans-are-smart-2.jpg 1252w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-fans-are-smart-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-fans-are-smart-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-fans-are-smart-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-fans-are-smart-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3491508" class="wp-caption-text"> 《Starfield》来源：Xbox Games Studios</figcaption></figure><p>对于一些<em>Starfield</em>粉丝来说，这一举动并不受欢迎。作为回应，其中一位免费重新上传了没有 DRM 保护的 DLSS 3 mod。</p><p> “我确实认为，如果改装者愿意，他们应该从他们的工作中赚到一些钱。建造这些需要大量的技巧和奉献精神，为此收费并没有什么错，” <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/pcgaming/comments/169bgun/comment/jz2159e/?utm_source=reddit&amp;utm_medium=web2x&amp;context=3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">一位玩家说道</a>。</p><p> “我的看法是，模组是衍生作品，你不能靠它赚钱，它不是你的财产，” <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/pcgaming/comments/169bgun/comment/jz2711h/?utm_source=reddit&amp;utm_medium=web2x&amp;context=3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">另一位回复道</a>。这场争论让人想起 2015 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-elder-scrolls-5-skyrim"><em>《天际</em></a>》付费模组的争议，当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bethesda">贝塞斯达</a>收回了在模组制作者、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/valve">Valve</a>和自己之间分配模组收入的计划。</p><p>由于<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/amd">AMD</a>和Bethesda就这款角色扮演游戏的PC移植达成协议， <em>Starfield</em>仅支持AMD自己的FSR（FidelityFX超分辨率）技术。这提升了<em>Starfield</em>的视觉效果，在不牺牲细节和分辨率的情况下提高帧速率。不过，AMD 游戏主管 Frank Azor 表示，没有什么可以阻止开发商引入 Nvidia 的 DLSS。 </p><figure id="attachment_3477679" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3477679" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3477679" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-sandwich-pirate-producer-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-sandwich-pirate-producer-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-sandwich-pirate-producer-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-sandwich-pirate-producer-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-sandwich-pirate-producer-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-sandwich-pirate-producer-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-sandwich-pirate-producer-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3477679" class="wp-caption-text"> “星空”信用：贝塞斯达</figcaption></figure><p>“如果 Bethesda 希望将 DLSS 引入游戏中，我们会全力支持他们，”Azor 在接受<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/25/22372077/amd-starfield-dlss-fsr-exclusive-frank-azor" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>The Verge</em></a>采访时回答道。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <em>Palworld</em>的开发商在问答中透露了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-developer-talks-rimworld-inspiration-and-map-size-in-new-qa-3492231">这款反乌托邦生物收集游戏背后的灵感</a>，问答中收到了一千多个问题。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/starfield-dlss-mod-sparks-controversy-over-paid-modding-3492782">《Starfield》DLSS 模组</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上，引发了有关付费模组的争议。</p> ;
