-music-legend-dies-aged-56-3473863">于上个月（7 月 26 日）去世，享年 56 岁以来</a>，许多艺术家都通过演绎《Nothing Compares 2 U》来表达哀悼。 </p><figure id="attachment_3480013" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3480013" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3480013" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sinead-OConnor@200-x1270.jpg" alt="西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinead O&#39;Connor) 登台表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sinead-OConnor@200-x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sinead-OConnor@200-x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sinead-OConnor@200-x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sinead-OConnor@200-x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sinead-OConnor@200-x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sinead-OConnor@200-x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3480013" class="wp-caption-text">西尼德·奥康纳在舞台上表演。图片来源：Peter Pakvis/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-fall-out-boy-cover-nothing-compares-2-u-in-tribute-to-sinead-oconnor-3474325">Fall Out Boy 在最近的一场演出中翻唱了这首歌</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pnk-and-brandi-carlile-cover-nothing-compares-2-u-in-tribute-to-sinead-oconnor-3474214">Brandi Carlile 和 P!nk 在俄亥俄州辛辛那提表演了这首歌</a>。</p><p>这位已故歌手的歌迷也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sinead-oconnor-fans-gather-to-sing-nothing-compares-2-u-at-dublin-tribute-3475498">于七月聚集在都柏林，演唱了她的歌曲“Nothing Compares 2 U”</a>以纪念她。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies-aged-56-3473863">许多明星也在奥康纳去世后向她表示哀悼，</a>包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/garbage">垃圾</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-corgan">比利·科根</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/micha