pg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/they-were-giants-tour-rescheduled-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/they-were-giants-tour-rescheduled-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/they-were-giants-tour-rescheduled-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/they-might-be-giants">他们可能是巨人队</a>宣布，由于健康原因，他们将推迟即将到来的英国、爱尔兰和澳大利亚巡演。</p><p>这支纽约乐队原定于今年 10 月在澳大利亚进行一系列演出，随后于 11 月在英国和爱尔兰演出，他们将完整演奏粉丝最喜爱的《Flood》。</p><p>继美国的 70 场演出门票全部售完后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/they-might-be-giants-announce-uk-tour-dates-2023-3413963">英国演出于 3 月份宣布</a>作为“Evening With”巡演的一部分。</p><p>然而，乐队今天（9 月 4 日）宣布，由于“迫在眉睫的健康问题”，他们即将举行的 2023 年巡演日期将重新安排。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="zxx" dir="ltr"> <a href="https://t.co/C0lH2vEEyP">pic.twitter.com/C0lH2vEEyP</a></p><p> — 他们可能是巨人 (@tmbg) <a href="https://twitter.com/tmbg/status/1698563177292640545?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 4 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>他们在社交帖子中分享了这一消息，并写道：“这些暂时的并发症应该在未来几个月内得到解决。我们热切期待明年即将举行的这些演出（这是我们能够通过巡回演出的连续性确保演出的最早时间）。</p><p> “是的，这些仍然是超豪华的《An Evening with》节目，有两套，包括全部《Flood》。”</p><p>他们的结论是“对给您带来的不便表示诚挚的歉意，非常感谢您的耐心等待。”</p><p>该帖子还确认，当前门票在新日期仍然有效。您可以在<a href="https://www.theymightbegiants.com/shows" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“他们可能是巨人”的网站</a>上找到重新安排的日期。 </p><figure id="attachment_3413975" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3413975" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3413975" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/They-Might-Be-Giants-onstage@2000x1270.jpg" alt="他们可能是巨人" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/They-Might-Be-Giants-onstage@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/They-Might-Be-Giants-onstage@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/They-Might-Be-Giants-onstage@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/They-Might-Be-Giants-onstage@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/They-Might-Be-Giants-onstage@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/They-Might-Be-Giants-onstage@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3413975" class="wp-caption-text">他们可能是巨人。图片来源：David A. Smith/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>这些演出也是为了庆祝乐队于 2021 年发行的最新专辑《Book》。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hear-might-giants-new-album-like-fun-2218046">Upon releasing their 2018 album &#39;I Like Fun&#39;</a> , <em>NME</em> described the 15-track LP as “their most diverse and sonically adventurous work to date”.</p><p> They Might Be Giants are known for their legendary <em>Malcolm In The Middle</em> theme song &#39;Boss Of Me&#39; and indie radio anthem &#39;Birdhouse In Your Soul&#39;.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/they-might-be-giants-postpone-uk-ireland-and-australia-tours-due-to-health-reasons-3492770">They Might Be Giants postpone UK, Ireland and Australia tours due to health reasons</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
